flowchart LR
    A[Developer Commit Code] --> B[Jenkins Pipeline Local]
    B --> C[Maven Build]
    C --> D[OWASP Dependency-Check]
    D --> E{CVSS >= 7?}
    E -- Yes --> F[Fail/Unstable Build]
    E -- No --> G[Pass Build]
    F --> H[HTML Vulnerability Report]
    G --> H
    H --> I[Fix Dependency Version]
    I --> D
